Living, kitchen and dining feature 9' ceilings and will make your next party a hit! Large fireplace with media space for the big screen. Master bedroom features large walk-in closet and seperate soaker tub and shower. Head upstairs to the bonus room for the ideal media room or home office. Garage door opener not included. RCE-923.
